---
import Link from "../../components/General/Link.astro";
import ProjectCats from "../../components/Project/Project-Cats.astro";
import ToolCard from "../../components/Project/Tool-Card.astro";
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import PhotoSwipeImage from "../../components/General/PhotoSwipeImage.astro";
---

<Layout title="Hunter | Banking">
  <main class="container flex flex-col">
    <section class="hero-section container">
      <Link arrowOnLeft text="projects" url="" />
      <div class="container-name">
        <h1 class="mt-4 text-sans-bold flex flex-col md:flex-row">
          <p class="primary-header">Consumer Banking</p>
        </h1>
      </div>
      <div class="container-project-cats mt-5 flex flex-row">
        <ProjectCats color="#339288" title="UI Design" />
        <ProjectCats color="#339288" title="Product Design" />
        <ProjectCats color="#339288" title="UX Engineering" />
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="section-description grid mt-8 mb-20">
      <div class="container-description text-sans">
        <div class="container-description__description">
          <p class="description">
            A comprehensive UI and UX overhaul of the flagship ProcessMaker
            consumer bank account opening solution
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <section class="section-goal">
        <div class="container-goal">
          <div class="container-goal__tools">
            <ToolCard
              url="/svg/tools-figma.svg"
              ,
              title="Figma"
              ,
              content="Modern UI Design tool"
            />
            <ToolCard
              url="/svg/tools-sass.svg"
              ,
              title="SASS"
              ,
              content="Digital Collaboration "
            />

            <ToolCard
              url="/svg/tools-jira.svg"
              ,
              title="Jira"
              ,
              content="Agile Project Management"
            />

            <ToolCard
              url="/svg/tools-chrome.svg"
              ,
              title="DevTools"
              ,
              content="For interaction design testing"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="container-goal__goal">
            <div class="goal-header text-sans-bold">
              <h2 class="secondary-header">The Goal</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="goal-text text-sans">
              <p>
                There were three primary objectives in the re-design: improving
                the tool's approachability, reducing the cognitive load placed
                on users, and implementing modern design patterns that will
                enable us to expand on the tool's functionality in the future.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="section-challenge lg:mt-20 mb-20">
        <div class="container-challenge grid">
          <div class="container-challenge__challenge">
            <div class="challenge-header text-sans-bold">
              <h2 class="secondary-header">Cognitive Load</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="challenge-text text-sans">
              <p>
                The project aims to lower cognitive load for users navigating
                the inherent complexities of BPMN by minimizing visual clutter,
                simplifying the interface, and implementing modern UI design
                paradigms. We intend to enhance user experience through
                intuitive design, logical feature organization, and maximizing
                canvas workspace, thus enabling easier interaction and reducing
                the mental effort required for diagram creation. By adopting
                strategies like modular menus and progressive disclosure, we
                focus on presenting only necessary information, making the tool
                more approachable and efficient, and allowing users to
                concentrate on their modeling tasks without unnecessary
                distractions.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="container-challenge__image flex flex-col space-y-20">
            <!-- <PhotoSwipeImage
              alt=""
              image={{
                src: whitespace.src,
                width: 2128,
                height: 1091,
                thumbnail: whitespace.src,
              }}
            /> -->
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="section-challenge">
        <div class="container-challenge-cont">
          <div class="container-challenge-cont__image flex flex-col space-y-20">
            <!-- <PhotoSwipeImage
              alt=""
              image={{
                src: builder.src,
                width: 2213,
                height: 1796,
                thumbnail: builder.src,
              }}
            /> -->
          </div>
          <div class="container-challenge-cont__challenge">
            <div class="challenge-text text-sans">
              <div class="challenge-header text-sans-bold">
                <h2 class="secondary-header">A Design System</h2>
              </div>
              <p>
                The project necessitated the creation of a design system to
                streamline and unify the development process, enhancing
                collaboration between designers and developers. By establishing
                a consistent set of design principles and components, the system
                fostered a cohesive user experience and accelerated the
                design-to-development workflow. Leveraging a design system
                empowered the team to iterate more efficiently, ensuring that
                changes were uniformly applied across the tool, reducing
                redundancy and miscommunication. This cohesive approach not only
                sped up project timelines but also ensured that the tool
                remained scalable and adaptable to future enhancements, making
                it a critical investment for the project's long-term success and
                maintainability.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </section>
  </main>

  <style>
    .img_screen {
      border-radius: 4px;
    }

    .primary-header {
      line-height: 0.8;
      font-size: 5rem;
    }

    .secondary-header {
      font-size: 3rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 1000px) {
      .primary-header {
        font-size: 14.06vw;
      }
      .primary-header p:last-child {
        margin-top: 1rem;
      }
      .secondary-header {
        font-size: 9vw;
        white-space: nowrap;
      }
    }

    .section-description {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(12, 1fr);
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .description {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .container-description {
      display: grid;
      grid-column: 1 / 13;
    }

    .container-project-cats {
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
      .container-description {
        grid-column: 1 / 10;
      }
    }

    .container-challenge-cont__image {
      order: 2;
    }

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
      .container-challenge-cont__image {
        order: 1;
      }
      .container-challenge-cont__challenge {
        order: 2;
      }
    }

    .container-goal,
    .container-challenge-cont {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 20px;
    }

    @media (min-width: 1000px) {
      .container-goal,
      .container-challenge-cont {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr;
      }
    }

    .container-goal__tools {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      column-gap: 1rem;
      row-gap: 2rem;
      order: 1;
      margin: 2rem 0;
    }

    @media (min-width: 1000px) {
      .container-goal__tools {
        order: 0;
        margin: unset;
      }
    }

    .container-challenge {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 30px;
    }

    @media (min-width: 1000px) {
      .container-challenge {
        grid-template-columns: 2fr 2fr;
      }
    }

    .byline {
      padding: 0.1rem 0;
      animation-delay: 1s;
      animation: transitionLeft 1s;
      font-size: 3rem;
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .stagger {
      animation: transitionLeft 1.3s;
    }

    /* ANIMATIONS */

    @keyframes transitionIn {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(10px);
      }
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }

    @keyframes transitionLeft {
      0% {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateX(-5px);
      }
      80% {
        transform: translateX(3px);
      }
      100% {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateX(0);
      }
    }

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
      #links-section {
        flex-direction: row;
      }
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
